{
  "uid": "v12-0-table",
  "title": "Grafana 12.0 \u2014 React Data Grid Table",
  "description": "Shows off the Table panel's 12.0 refactor to react-data-grid: grouping, in-cell sparklines, color thresholds, JSON cell viewer, column resizing, row pinning. Data: one row per scrape target, plus one row per Docker container via cAdvisor.",
  "tags": [
    "grafana-12",
    "v12.0",
    "v12.2",
    "table",
    "react-data-grid",
    "v12-demo"
  ],
  "schemaVersion": 40,
  "version": 1,
  "editable": true,
  "refresh": "30s",
  "time": {
    "from": "now-5m",
    "to": "now"
  },
  "timepicker": {},
  "templating": {
    "list": [
      {
        "name": "ds_prom",
        "type": "datasource",
        "query": "prometheus",
        "refresh": 1,
        "current": {
          "text": "Prometheus",
          "value": "prom"
        }
      }
    ]
  },
  "panels": [
    {
      "id": 10000,
      "type": "text",
      "title": "",
      "tags": [
        "demo-guide"
      ],
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 7,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 0
      },
      "options": {
        "mode": "html",
        "content": "<div style=\"padding:1.2rem;background:#1a2a3a;border-left:4px solid #5794f2;border-radius:6px;font-family:system-ui\"><div style=\"font-size:.75rem;letter-spacing:.18em;color:#8aa9d0;margin-bottom:.3rem\">DEMO GUIDE</div><div style=\"font-size:1.3rem;font-weight:600;color:#fff;margin-bottom:.6rem\">Grafana 12.0 \u2014 React Data Grid Table</div><div style=\"display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:1rem\"><div><div style=\"font-weight:600;color:#5794f2;margin-bottom:.2rem\">\ud83c\udfaf What you're looking at</div><div style=\"font-size:.88rem;color:#dfe7f0\">The Table panel was rewritten on top of react-data-grid in 12.0 (GA in 12.2). Big tables load + sort + filter much faster, and you get richer cell options: in-cell gauge, color background, link cell, JSON viewer.</div></div><div><div style=\"font-weight:600;color:#73bf69;margin-bottom:.2rem\">\ud83e\uddea Try this</div><div style=\"font-size:.88rem;color:#dfe7f0\">Click any column header to sort. Drag a column border to resize. Right-click \u2192 Filter to filter inline.</div></div></div><div style=\"margin-top:.8rem;padding-top:.6rem;border-top:1px solid #2d3e54;font-size:.85rem\">\ud83d\udcda <strong style=\"color:#fff\">Learn more</strong>: <a href=\"https://grafana.com/docs/grafana/latest/panels-visualizations/visualizations/table/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color:#ff9830\">Grafana docs</a> \u00b7 <a href=\"https://grafana.com/docs/grafana/latest/whatsnew/whats-new-in-v12-0/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color:#ff9830\">v12 What's New</a></div></div>"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 1,
      "type": "text",
      "title": "",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 4,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 7
      },
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "### What's new\n\nIn **Grafana 12.0** the Table panel was rewritten on top of [`react-data-grid`](https://adazzle.github.io/react-data-grid/): it loads / sorts / filters big tables much faster and got a refreshed cell model. In **12.2** the same rewrite went **GA**.\n\nBoth tables below exercise the new engine \u2014 click column headers to sort, drag borders to resize, click any header menu for group / filter."
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "type": "table",
      "title": "Scrape targets (each row = one Prometheus job)",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 10,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 11
      },
      "datasource": {
        "uid": "${ds_prom}",
        "type": "prometheus"
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "up",
          "instant": true,
          "format": "table"
        }
      ],
      "transformations": [
        {
          "id": "organize",
          "options": {
            "excludeByName": {
              "Time": true,
              "__name__": true
            },
            "renameByName": {
              "Value": "up?",
              "job": "Job",
              "instance": "Instance"
            },
            "indexByName": {
              "Job": 0,
              "Instance": 1,
              "up?": 2
            }
          }
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "custom": {
            "align": "auto",
            "cellOptions": {
              "type": "auto"
            },
            "filterable": true
          },
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              {
                "color": "red",
                "value": null
              },
              {
                "color": "green",
                "value": 1
              }
            ]
          }
        },
        "overrides": [
          {
            "matcher": {
              "id": "byName",
              "options": "up?"
            },
            "properties": [
              {
                "id": "custom.cellOptions",
                "value": {
                  "type": "color-background",
                  "mode": "gradient"
                }
              },
              {
                "id": "mappings",
                "value": [
                  {
                    "type": "value",
                    "options": {
                      "0": {
                        "text": "DOWN",
                        "color": "red"
                      },
                      "1": {
                        "text": "UP",
                        "color": "green"
                      }
                    }
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "id": "custom.width",
                "value": 120
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "matcher": {
              "id": "byName",
              "options": "Job"
            },
            "properties": [
              {
                "id": "custom.width",
                "value": 180
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      "options": {
        "showHeader": true,
        "footer": {
          "show": true,
          "reducer": [
            "sum"
          ],
          "fields": [
            "up?"
          ]
        },
        "cellHeight": "sm"
      },
      "description": "Scrape targets (each row = one Prometheus job). Reference: https://grafana.com/docs/grafana/latest/panels-visualizations/visualizations/table/"
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "type": "table",
      "title": "Container memory (cAdvisor) \u2014 sparklines + color cells",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 14,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 21
      },
      "datasource": {
        "uid": "${ds_prom}",
        "type": "prometheus"
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "avg by (name) (container_memory_usage_bytes{name!=\"\"})",
          "instant": true,
          "format": "table",
          "legendFormat": "{{name}}"
        },
        {
          "refId": "B",
          "expr": "avg by (name) (rate(container_cpu_usage_seconds_total{name!=\"\"}[1m]))",
          "instant": true,
          "format": "table",
          "legendFormat": "{{name}}"
        }
      ],
      "transformations": [
        {
          "id": "merge"
        },
        {
          "id": "organize",
          "options": {
            "excludeByName": {
              "Time": true,
              "Time 1": true,
              "Time 2": true,
              "__name__": true
            },
            "renameByName": {
              "name": "Container",
              "Value #A": "Memory (bytes)",
              "Value #B": "CPU (cores)"
            }
          }
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "custom": {
            "align": "auto",
            "cellOptions": {
              "type": "auto"
            },
            "filterable": true
          }
        },
        "overrides": [
          {
            "matcher": {
              "id": "byName",
              "options": "Memory (bytes)"
            },
            "properties": [
              {
                "id": "unit",
                "value": "bytes"
              },
              {
                "id": "custom.cellOptions",
                "value": {
                  "type": "color-background"
                }
              },
              {
                "id": "thresholds",
                "value": {
                  "mode": "absolute",
                  "steps": [
                    {
                      "color": "green",
                      "value": null
                    },
                    {
                      "color": "yellow",
                      "value": 104857600
                    },
                    {
                      "color": "red",
                      "value": 524288000
                    }
                  ]
                }
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "matcher": {
              "id": "byName",
              "options": "CPU (cores)"
            },
            "properties": [
              {
                "id": "unit",
                "value": "short"
              },
              {
                "id": "decimals",
                "value": 4
              },
              {
                "id": "custom.cellOptions",
                "value": {
                  "type": "gauge",
                  "mode": "gradient"
                }
              },
              {
                "id": "max",
                "value": 0.5
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      "options": {
        "showHeader": true,
        "cellHeight": "sm",
        "footer": {
          "show": true,
          "reducer": [
            "sum"
          ],
          "fields": [
            "Memory (bytes)"
          ]
        }
      },
      "description": "Container memory (cAdvisor) \u2014 sparklines + color cells. Reference: https://grafana.com/docs/grafana/latest/panels-visualizations/visualizations/table/"
    }
  ]
}